eferred.Hours, Salary &amp; Benefits:29.50/hour with benefits as per the CUPE Collective Agreement. Full-time (35 hours per week) Monday 10 am – 6 pm, Tuesday-Friday 9 am – 5 pm.Please submit resumes with cover letters to Alex Seaborn director@castlegarlibrary.com Closing Date: January 22, 2024 Compensation 29.50 Closes: 22 January, 2024 Castlegar &amp; District Public Library Castlegar , BC Policies and Terms of Use · jobboard@bcla.bc.ca / BCLA PO BOX 19008, Rocky Point PO, Port Moody, BC V3H 0J1 window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
